"        Pigors M, Kiritsi D, Kr&uuml;mpelmann S, et al. Lack of plakoglobin leads to lethal congenital epidermolysis bullosa: a novel clinico-genetic entity. Hum Mol Genet 2011; 20:1811.",
"       </li>",
