"        Fine JD. General cutaneous manifestations. In: Life with Epidermolysis Bullosa (EB): Etiology, diagnosis, multidisciplinary care and therapy, Fine JD, Hintner H (Eds), Springer, Wien, New York 2008. p.99.&nbsp;&nbsp;",
"       </li>",
