"       </li>",
"       <li>",
"        Nakano A, Pulkkinen L, Murrell D, et al. Epidermolysis bullosa with congenital pyloric atresia: novel mutations in the beta 4 integrin gene (ITGB4) and genotype/phenotype correlations. Pediatr Res 2001; 49:618.",
"       </li>",
"       <li>",
"        Pulkkinen L, Kim DU, Uitto J. Epidermolysis bullosa with pyloric atresia: Novel mutations in the beta4 integrin gene (ITGB4). Am J Pathol 1998; 152:157.",
"       </li>",
